desc: A small local, professional and reliable business that is passionate about gardening. With qualifications and over 7 years experience in garden maintenance & horticulture. Services include lawn mowing, regular garden maintenance, garden blitz's, hedge trimming, seasonal jobs such as pruning or lawn scarifying & more!

layout.text: We are a small business working in and around the Maidstone area. We believe our success is built on our core fundamentals of being hardworking, reliable & incredibly friendly!
